<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I&apos;m a bit late, but I cried at the ending. Not sure if they were tears of joy or sadness. But it was beautiful either way.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I'm a bit late, but I cried at the ending. Not sure if they were tears of joy or sadness. But it was beautiful either way.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
